{"tid":2128764,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣封關鎖國封中國超慘　一片繁榮穩定大眾開心　生育率都創新高","createTime":"2020-07-28T07:09:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-28T10:28:31.000Z","uid":261647,"like":30,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"150dc772f9f0a1ef066d43964ab2abbe3cf41c73","tid":2128764,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T07:09:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/yochang.chen/posts/3680550365292402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fyochang.chen%2Fposts%2F3680550365292402&d=oFI5KSBgBGvHra6dYUznBrXdyKWV89KwSxbYnQ5zRIM%3D&h=023f0a69\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/yochang.chen/posts/3680550365292402</a><br />\n<br />\n作者：陳祐瑲<br />\n<br />\n問：台灣一旦鎖國，下場會有多淒慘？<br />\n<br />\n答：股市上萬點創新高，出口成長居亞洲四小龍之首，飯店旅舍爆滿報復性觀光，房市熱錢強強滾...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n陳祐瑲:<br />\n真的太淒慘了！ <a href=\"https://today.line.me/TW/article/X8j6Pe\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftoday.line.me%2FTW%2Farticle%2FX8j6Pe&d=oFI5KSBgBGvHra6dYUznBrXdyKWV89KwSxbYnQ5zRIM%3D&h=43237dc5\" target=\"_blank\">https://today.line.me/TW/article/X8j6Pe</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sGHmtYO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsGHmtYO.png&h=0212a514&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPolly Hsieh:<br />\n7-8月一房難求⋯心好累<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n8OT4LM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn8OT4LM.png&h=53a9db67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n陳祐瑲:<br />\n只好開TESLA開冷氣全家睡車上了<br />\n<br />\nVincent Chou:<br />\n這樣不會沒電嗎？推車到充電站？<br />\n<br />\n陳祐瑲:<br />\n只能夜宿超充站附近了<br />\n<br />\nVincent Chou:<br />\n結果Tesla車主也都這樣想，充電也要排隊，好慘！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nMia Liu:<br />\n真的是太淒慘了啦....八月訂不到房間<br />\n<br />\nJudy Su:<br />\n中秋也難訂了啦～只好反向操作住台北的商務性的國際酒店，至少可以享受設施<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ndog2xW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNdog2xW.png&h=37fc17aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n陳祐瑲:<br />\n一語驚醒夢中人<br />\n<br />\nJudy Su:<br />\n不要跟我們搶（轉身去開電腦<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ndog2xW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNdog2xW.png&h=37fc17aa&s={SIZE}\" />）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nYuJun Hsieh:<br />\n居然是事實，完全不能反駁<br />\n<br />\n陳祐瑲:<br />\n下一題：「陸客不來了，台灣下場會有多淒慘？」<br />\n<br />\nYuJun Hsieh:<br />\n答：墾丁大街、花東各地民宿飯店被遊客擠爆。澎湖已經在規勸遊客們暫時不要前往。<br />\n<br />\n李定家:<br />\n非常悽慘，週四晚連訂三家餐廳都滿席<br />\n<br />\nYuJun Hsieh:<br />\n結論：國家機器動的很厲害，製造出來的幻象，其實整個台灣已經又老又窮。年輕人又不工作⋯⋯整組都壞了~<br />\n<br />\nVincent Chou:<br />\n韓總機上身嗎<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Addpr0h.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAddpr0h.png&h=302a3174&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nTing-Jui Kang:<br />\n我猜可能連去爬個山都要排隊&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\nKuo Ching Chang: 已經在排隊了⋯QQ<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPinwei Huang:<br />\n百貨公司好多人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nMike Liu:<br />\n振興券一堆券罵聲越大用越猛<br />\n<br />\n鄧美菁:<br />\n嫌貨才是買貨人啊<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2AsmudY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2AsmudY.png&h=91928a53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n蕭佑竹: 電影院爆滿<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nJames Li:<br />\n鎖國好像也沒有像中國國民黨講的那麼糟糕...<br />\n<br />\nLynn Tsao:<br />\n他們的不鎖國其實也只有對中國開放而已<br />\n<br />\n陳錦華:<br />\n<br />\n台灣一直以來都沒有鎖國，除了疫情需要的這陣子對於觀光「有條件的鎖國」<br />\n<br />\n中國國民黨的鎖國不是台灣對全世界鎖國，而是指台灣對中國鎖國，可是這也不是事實，因為台商一直有，對中國的進出口也一直有（經濟部資料可以查）<br />\n<br />\n他們中國國民黨只是像韓總機那樣，利用人云亦云的人性傳播錯誤訊息（造謠），以便達到目的。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nFrance Nien:<br />\n昨晚台積電ADR又漲了近10%，下週開盤應該很精彩⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nNotshrm Liao: 真心覺得扯<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nVincent Chou:<br />\n<br />\n超慘，都不敢出門玩了<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tDVZ0k0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtDVZ0k0.png&h=dc8bcfd5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tDVZ0k0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtDVZ0k0.png&h=dc8bcfd5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tDVZ0k0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtDVZ0k0.png&h=dc8bcfd5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n房價更高買不起，出門到處都塞車，餐廳都客滿，股票說好的撿便宜咧？一年後出生率創新高，又推升一堆東西漲價，真的很慘！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n木華:<br />\n不只如此，出生率也新高啊！<br />\n<br />\nVincent Chou:<br />\n一年後的新聞<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wxpW2zN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwxpW2zN.png&h=07258868&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n黃語熙:<br />\n鎖國個頭= =<br />\n<a href=\"https://money.udn.com/money/story/5612/4716007\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmoney.udn.com%2Fmoney%2Fstory%2F5612%2F4716007&d=oFI5KSBgBGvHra6dYUznBrXdyKWV89KwSxbYnQ5zRIM%3D&h=269cf737\" target=\"_blank\">https://money.udn.com/money/story/5612/4716007</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rQ2d4HD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrQ2d4HD.png&h=46a427b1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3ebba3245a0cc48583837881984489e1e3378263","tid":2128764,"uid":179729,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T07:21:48.000Z","msg":"tst都少左蝗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73d3b0ef449c95f11e55c514d58eb8942b451e26","tid":2128764,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T08:03:47.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba8dbe03a06e67836d350ffd5f853f6e517e42c5","tid":2128764,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T08:04:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c114832072132c823c34c8cbfdef1d20e9269be","tid":212